data.description: Price Reduction!! Do Not Miss this Beautiful 3bd 2ba OPEN FLOORPLAN  home on a Full Acre Lot.  Bring your toys and RV! This home features a New Roof, New Laminate Flooring, Newer Blinds, and ceiling fans throughout the home.  You will enjoy the large pantry in the kitchen with a lot of storage and counter space.  The living room has a beautiful Stone Fireplace to enjoy on the cold nights and outside you will enjoy the new covered patio in the warmer weather.  The master suit has nice bathroom with double sinks and a large walk in closet.   Outside you have a nicely fenced front yard with a half circle drive, in the back yard you have a cross fenced lot for RV parking and room to put a workshop.  This home is very clean ready to move in!
